  APPENDIX: How to apply the Apache License to your project.

 To apply the Apache License to your project, open your project in a text editor and add the following:

    1. Include a copy of this License in a file named "LICENSE" in your project.

    2. Include the following statement in each file of your project:
    
        "Copyright [YYYY] [name of copyright owner]"
    
    For example:
    "Copyright 2026 chaotien"

    3. If your project includes a README file, include a summary of the License there as well.